{"tid":557861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打試過咁樣？","createTime":"2018-02-11T17:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T17:22:34.000Z","uid":142906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1afa5fbf92a20697eec1db0fe33c194fab2a2239","tid":557861,"uid":142906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:21:06.000Z","msg":"部ps4唔知做咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我攞去fd屋企玩插完線開機黑mon冇反應<br />\n跟住重開幾次有返畫面<br />\n之後又突然跳返黑mon，跟住手掣自動熄咗，機冇熄<br />\n之後我熄機重新插過d線就變咗咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/12/011822_ed03d4e5926cb72d1b154f6671dca875.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F12%2F011822_ed03d4e5926cb72d1b154f6671dca875.png&h=fa3e4b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n情況大概係咁我冇影低<br />\n之後佢就狂loop個safe mode<br />\n我返到屋企都係同樣情況<br />\n有冇巴打都有咁嘅情況出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：上網睇d外國forum都有咁嘅情況出現，好似話係更新咗5.0就變到咁，playstation未有解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc04e280c9e8c27ee81f45c75aa7e4270a3296c","tid":557861,"uid":24750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T17:22:34.000Z","msg":"未試過"}]}